member.summary:
Additional context properties specific to the invocation source.
Examples:
- VSCode: { "vscodeVersion": "1.85.0", "workspaceFolder": "/path/to/workspace" }
- GitHub Actions: { "GITHUB_REPOSITORY": "org/repo", "GITHUB_RUN_ID": "12345" }
- Jenkins: { "BUILD_NUMBER": "42", "JOB_NAME": "nightly-scan" }
